Far Manager
files and archives manager in Windows operating systems
  https://farmanager.com/
  https://github.com/FarGroup/FarManager

Colorer Library
a syntax highlighting and text parsing library
  https://github.com/colorer

Syntax and color schemes for colorer library
  https://github.com/colorer/Colorer-schemes

-------------------------------------------------------------
Resources location

system's Far Manager syntax highlighting files are placed into dir:
  C:\Program Files\Far Manager\Plugins\FarColorer\base\hrc\auto
